{"tid":868311,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"十月新番 INGRESS THE ANIMATION","createTime":"2018-10-19T10:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T13:12:40.000Z","uid":113000,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"58fd15c01d2d387bab80f08512dab591a16a8358","tid":868311,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ingressanime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2F&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4f4d5f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://ingressanime.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ingressanime.com/images/ogp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2Fimages%2Fogp2.jpg&h=237cdb9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4379da8f9934b0948243fe9fc32fb119e66b6c97","tid":868311,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fd15c01d2d387bab80f08512dab591a16a8358","tid":868311,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ingressanime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2F&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4f4d5f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://ingressanime.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ingressanime.com/images/ogp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2Fimages%2Fogp2.jpg&h=237cdb9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"依隻驚都有アニメ？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ab173817d81063b2832e4cf954181b7b6c0072","tid":868311,"uid":113000,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4379da8f9934b0948243fe9fc32fb119e66b6c97","tid":868311,"uid":45332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fd15c01d2d387bab80f08512dab591a16a8358","tid":868311,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T10:59:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ingressanime.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2F&d=WXSjg9b4xvSczAxs9sVyRcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=4f4d5f40\" target=\"_blank\">http://ingressanime.com/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://ingressanime.com/images/ogp2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fingressanime.com%2Fimages%2Fogp2.jpg&h=237cdb9f&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"依隻驚都有アニメ？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"《Ingress》動畫 10 月 Netflix 開播，EVA 班底參與<br />\n<br />\n日本富士電視台公布以 Niantic 開發的虛擬實境手機遊戲《Ingress》為題材的動畫《Ingress》，預計 10 月在富士電視台開播，並於 Netflix 與全球觀眾見面。<br />\n<br />\n今年 3 月富士電視台公布動畫版《Ingress: The Animation》，由《Pok&eacute;mon GO》遊戲 CG 設計櫻木優平擔任總監，《新世紀福音戰士 EVA》作畫監督本田雄任人物設定。日版聲優方面，由中島良樹飾演 Makoto（誠）、上田麗奈飾 Sarah、喜田茂雄飾演新角色 Jack。原作遊戲飾演「ADA」AI 人工智能的緒方惠美，將於動畫繼續出演。至於英文版演員陣容有待公布。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲故事背景方面，將講述自幼擁有觸摸物體就能讀取記憶能力的 Makoto，在一次實驗室爆炸意外中，發現未知物質「XM」的存在。他要讀取倖存者 Sarah 手上的戒指，讀取部分記憶。人類精神有重大影響的物質「MX」將捲入「天啟者」與「反抗軍」兩大陣營的鬥爭。<br />\n<br />\n動畫播放將配合《Ingress》新手機遊戲《Ingress Prime》推出，遊戲將用到《Ingress》的背景設定與人物設計，使用與《Pok&eacute;mon GO》相同的技術與遊戲平台，再加上動畫版的新人物。製作小組吸收了初代《Ingress》與《Pok&eacute;mon GO》的經驗之後，《Ingress Prime》將會以全新方式展示。"},{"pid":"b22212b11902517b83a5523b95a70a823df908fa","tid":868311,"uid":147292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T12:00:34.000Z","msg":"有 Netflix 真係好幸福"},{"pid":"20c18d888e3020125b5ab10e4cc4b3ee62e32429","tid":868311,"uid":1678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T13:33:00.000Z","msg":"好睇"},{"pid":"ca79118789da43efc7b32bed65cd93f5c20689a8","tid":868311,"uid":4618,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T03:14:52.000Z","msg":"睇咗一集比想像中正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae20a2746e7fdade72a78e7f1db261268f37602e","tid":868311,"uid":56649,"like"